   "id": "b1",
   "titulo": "Pregunta 1 · Sistemas eléctricos y electrónicos",
   "color": "#f59e0b",
   "descripcion_tarjeta": "Sistema de alarma de un depósito de gas con cuatro sensores: tabla de verdad, canónica, Karnaugh y circuito.",
   "svg_tarjeta": "<svg viewBox='0 0 90 60' fill='none' stroke='#f59e0b' stroke-width='3'><path d='M45 12l16 28H29z'/><path d='M45 24v8M45 36v2'/></svg>",
   "cuestiones": [
    {
     "id": "q1",
     "titulo": "Pregunta 1 · Alarma de un depósito de gas (lógica)",
     "etiqueta": "SISTEMAS ELÉCTRICOS",
     "menu": "P1 · Alarma (lógica 4 variables)",
     "titulo_corto": "P1",
     "meta": "Pregunta única y obligatoria · 2,5 puntos (a: 1,0 · b: 0,5 · c: 0,5 · d: 0,5)",
     "enunciado_html": "<p>Un depósito de gas propano tiene cuatro sensores: temperatura (A), presión (B), nivel (C) y peso/masa (D); a valor alto le corresponde &laquo;1&raquo; y a valor bajo &laquo;0&raquo;. La alarma S actúa cuando:</p><ul><li>Alta temperatura, bajo nivel y alto peso.</li><li>Alta temperatura, bajo nivel y bajo peso.</li><li>Alta temperatura, alta presión y alto nivel.</li><li>Baja temperatura, alta presión y bajo nivel.</li></ul><ol type='a'><li>Elaborar la tabla de verdad. <span class='pts'>(1 punto)</span></li><li>Función lógica en primera forma canónica. <span class='pts'>(0,5 puntos)</span></li><li>Simplificar por Karnaugh. <span class='pts'>(0,5 puntos)</span></li><li>Representar el circuito lógico. <span class='pts'>(0,5 puntos)</span></li></ol>",
     "figura_enunciado_svg": "",
     "aplica_html": "<p>Traducimos cada condición a variables (las no citadas son &laquo;don't care&raquo;, cubren ambos valores). La primera forma canónica es la suma de minterms con S=1 y el mapa de Karnaugh de 4 variables permite agrupar y simplificar.</p>",
     "solucion_html": "<h5>a) Tabla de verdad</h5><p>Las dos primeras condiciones se resumen en <b>A alta y C bajo</b> (peso indiferente). S=1 en los minterms 4, 5, 8, 9, 12, 13, 14 y 15:</p><table class='dat'><tr><th>A</th><th>B</th><th>C</th><th>D</th><th>S</th></tr><tr><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>0</td></tr><tr><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>1</td><td>0</td></tr><tr><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>1</td><td>0</td><td>0</td></tr><tr><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>0</td></tr><tr style='background:rgba(74,222,128,.14)'><td>0</td><td>1</td><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>1</td></tr><tr style='background:rgba(74,222,128,.14)'><td>0</td><td>1</td><td>0</td><td>1</td><td>1</td></tr><tr><td>0</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>0</td><td>0</td></tr><tr><td>0</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>0</td></tr><tr style='background:rgba(74,222,128,.14)'><td>1</td><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>1</td></tr><tr style='background:rgba(74,222,128,.14)'><td>1</td><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>1</td><td>1</td></tr><tr><td>1</td><td>0</td><td>1</td><td>0</td><td>0</td></tr><tr><td>1</td><td>0</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>0</td></tr><tr style='background:rgba(74,222,128,.14)'><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>1</td></tr><tr style='background:rgba(74,222,128,.14)'><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>0</td><td>1</td><td>1</td></tr><tr style='background:rgba(74,222,128,.14)'><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>0</td><td>1</td></tr><tr style='background:rgba(74,222,128,.14)'><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>1</td></tr></table><h5>b) Primera forma canónica</h5><div class='formula'>$$S=\\bar ABC\\bar D+\\bar ABC D+A\\bar B\\bar C\\bar D+A\\bar B\\bar CD+AB\\bar C\\bar D+AB\\bar CD+ABC\\bar D+ABCD$$</div><h5>c) Simplificación por Karnaugh</h5><figure class='fig'><svg viewBox='0 0 470 320' width='100%' style='max-width:430px;height:auto' fill='none' font-family='Inter,system-ui,sans-serif'><text x='110' y='58' fill='#94a3b8' font-size='12'>AB\\CD</text><text x='179' y='58' fill='#7dd3fc' font-size='13' text-anchor='middle'>00</text><text x='237' y='58' fill='#7dd3fc' font-size='13' text-anchor='middle'>01</text><text x='295' y='58' fill='#7dd3fc' font-size='13' text-anchor='middle'>11</text><text x='353' y='58' fill='#7dd3fc' font-size='13' text-anchor='middle'>10</text><text x='128' y='99' fill='#7dd3fc' font-size='13' text-anchor='middle'>00</text><rect x='150' y='72' width='58' height='44' fill='none' stroke='#334155' stroke-width='1.3'/><text x='179' y='100' fill='#64748b' font-size='17' font-weight='700' text-anchor='middle'>0</text><rect x='208' y='72' width='58' height='44' fill='none' stroke='#334155' stroke-width='1.3'/><text x='237' y='100' fill='#64748b' font-size='17' font-weight='700' text-anchor='middle'>0</text><rect x='266' y='72' width='58' height='44' fill='none' stroke='#334155' stroke-width='1.3'/><text x='295' y='100' fill='#64748b' font-size='17' font-weight='700' text-anchor='middle'>0</text><rect x='324' y='72' width='58' height='44' fill='none' stroke='#334155' stroke-width='1.3'/><text x='353' y='100' fill='#64748b' font-size='17' font-weight='700' text-anchor='middle'>0</text><text x='128' y='143' fill='#7dd3fc' font-size='13' text-anchor='middle'>01</text><rect x='150' y='116' width='58' height='44' fill='none' stroke='#334155' stroke-width='1.3'/><text x='179' y='144' fill='#4ade80' font-size='17' font-weight='700' text-anchor='middle'>1</text><rect x='208' y='116' width='58' height='44' fill='none' stroke='#334155' stroke-width='1.3'/><text x='237' y='144' fill='#4ade80' font-size='17' font-weight='700' text-anchor='middle'>1</text><rect x='266' y='116' width='58' height='44' fill='none' stroke='#334155' stroke-width='1.3'/><text x='295' y='144' fill='#64748b' font-size='17' font-weight='700' text-anchor='middle'>0</text><rect x='324' y='116' width='58' height='44' fill='none' stroke='#334155' stroke-width='1.3'/><text x='353' y='144' fill='#64748b' font-size='17' font-weight='700' text-anchor='middle'>0</text><text x='128' y='187' fill='#7dd3fc' font-size='13' text-anchor='middle'>11</text><rect x='150' y='160' width='58' height='44' fill='none' stroke='#334155' stroke-width='1.3'/><text x='179' y='188' fill='#4ade80' font-size='17' font-weight='700' text-anchor='middle'>1</text><rect x='208' y='160' width='58' height='44' fill='none' stroke='#334155' stroke-width='1.3'/><text x='237' y='188' fill='#4ade80' font-size='17' font-weight='700' text-anchor='middle'>1</text><rect x='266' y='160' width='58' height='44' fill='none' stroke='#334155' stroke-width='1.3'/><text x='295' y='188' fill='#4ade80' font-size='17' font-weight='700' text-anchor='middle'>1</text><rect x='324' y='160' width='58' height='44' fill='none' stroke='#334155' stroke-width='1.3'/><text x='353' y='188' fill='#4ade80' font-size='17' font-weight='700' text-anchor='middle'>1</text><text x='128' y='231' fill='#7dd3fc' font-size='13' text-anchor='middle'>10</text><rect x='150' y='204' width='58' height='44' fill='none' stroke='#334155' stroke-width='1.3'/><text x='179' y='232' fill='#4ade80' font-size='17' font-weight='700' text-anchor='middle'>1</text><rect x='208' y='204' width='58' height='44' fill='none' stroke='#334155' stroke-width='1.3'/><text x='237' y='232' fill='#4ade80' font-size='17' font-weight='700' text-anchor='middle'>1</text><rect x='266' y='204' width='58' height='44' fill='none' stroke='#334155' stroke-width='1.3'/><text x='295' y='232' fill='#64748b' font-size='17' font-weight='700' text-anchor='middle'>0</text><rect x='324' y='204' width='58' height='44' fill='none' stroke='#334155' stroke-width='1.3'/><text x='353' y='232' fill='#64748b' font-size='17' font-weight='700' text-anchor='middle'>0</text><rect x='146' y='156' width='124' height='96' rx='9' fill='none' stroke='#f59e0b' stroke-width='2.2'/><text x='204' y='266' fill='#fbbf24' font-size='13' text-anchor='middle'>A&#183;C&#773;</text><rect x='142' y='152' width='248' height='60' rx='11' fill='none' stroke='#a78bfa' stroke-width='2.2'/><text x='396' y='187' fill='#c4b5fd' font-size='13'>A&#183;B</text><rect x='152' y='118' width='112' height='84' rx='7' fill='none' stroke='#38bdf8' stroke-width='2.2' stroke-dasharray='5 3'/><text x='120' y='165' fill='#7dd3fc' font-size='13'>B&#183;C&#773;</text></svg><figcaption>Grupos A&#183;C&#773; (naranja), A&#183;B (violeta) y B&#183;C&#773; (azul). La variable D se elimina.</figcaption></figure><div class='formula'>$$S=A\\bar C+AB+B\\bar C$$</div><div class='res'><b>S = A·C&#773; + A·B + B·C&#773;</b></div><h5>d) Circuito lógico</h5><figure class='fig'><svg viewBox='0 0 500 300' width='100%' style='max-width:470px;height:auto' fill='none' font-family='Inter,system-ui,sans-serif' stroke='#e2e8f0' stroke-width='1.8'><text x='16' y='45' fill='#e2e8f0' font-size='14'>A</text><text x='16' y='120' fill='#e2e8f0' font-size='14'>B</text><text x='16' y='210' fill='#e2e8f0' font-size='14'>C</text><line x1='30' y1='205' x2='70' y2='205'/><polygon points='70,192 70,218 96,205' fill='none' stroke='#a78bfa' stroke-width='2'/><circle cx='101' cy='205' r='4' fill='none' stroke='#a78bfa' stroke-width='2'/><text x='108' y='198' fill='#c4b5fd' font-size='12'>C&#773;</text><path d='M200 30 L222.0 30 A20.0 20.0 0 0 1 222.0 70 L200 70 Z' fill='none' stroke='#38bdf8' stroke-width='2.2'/><line x1='30' y1='40' x2='200' y2='40'/><line x1='30' y1='120' x2='120' y2='120'/><line x1='120' y1='120' x2='120' y2='60'/><line x1='120' y1='60' x2='200' y2='60'/><line x1='242' y1='50' x2='300' y2='50'/><path d='M200 110 L222.0 110 A20.0 20.0 0 0 1 222.0 150 L200 150 Z' fill='none' stroke='#34d399' stroke-width='2.2'/><line x1='50' y1='40' x2='50' y2='130'/><line x1='50' y1='130' x2='200' y2='130'/><line x1='106' y1='205' x2='150' y2='205'/><line x1='150' y1='205' x2='150' y2='150'/><line x1='150' y1='150' x2='200' y2='150'/><line x1='242' y1='130' x2='300' y2='130'/><path d='M200 200 L222.0 200 A20.0 20.0 0 0 1 222.0 240 L200 240 Z' fill='none' stroke='#f59e0b' stroke-width='2.2'/><line x1='90' y1='120' x2='90' y2='210'/><line x1='90' y1='210' x2='200' y2='210'/><line x1='150' y1='205' x2='150' y2='230'/><line x1='150' y1='230' x2='200' y2='230'/><line x1='242' y1='220' x2='300' y2='220'/><path d='M300 30 Q350 30 400 135 Q350 240 300 240 Q328 135 300 30 Z' fill='none' stroke='#fb7185' stroke-width='2.2'/><line x1='300' y1='50' x2='318' y2='50'/><line x1='300' y1='130' x2='312' y2='130'/><line x1='300' y1='220' x2='318' y2='220'/><line x1='400' y1='135' x2='460' y2='135'/><text x='466' y='140' fill='#e2e8f0' font-size='15'>S</text></svg><figcaption>Tres puertas AND (una con C&#773;) y una OR de tres entradas.</figcaption></figure>"
