     "enunciado_html": "<p>La viga simplemente apoyada de la figura soporta una carga uniformemente distribuida de 200 N/m. Se pide:</p><ol type='a'><li>Ecuaciones de esfuerzos cortantes y momentos flectores. <span class='pts'>(1,25 puntos)</span></li><li>Dibujar los diagramas correspondientes. <span class='pts'>(1,25 puntos)</span></li></ol>",
     "figura_enunciado_svg": "<figure class='fig'><svg viewBox='0 0 620 290' width='100%' style='max-width:560px;height:auto' fill='none' font-family='Inter,system-ui,sans-serif'><text x='320' y='38' fill='#e2e8f0' font-size='16' text-anchor='middle'>Q = 200 N/m</text><line x1='95' y1='52' x2='545' y2='52' stroke='#f59e0b' stroke-width='2'/><line x1='95' y1='52' x2='95' y2='148' stroke='#f59e0b' stroke-width='1.5'/><polygon points='91,140 99,140 95,149' fill='#f59e0b'/><line x1='140' y1='52' x2='140' y2='148' stroke='#f59e0b' stroke-width='1.5'/><polygon points='136,140 144,140 140,149' fill='#f59e0b'/><line x1='185' y1='52' x2='185' y2='148' stroke='#f59e0b' stroke-width='1.5'/><polygon points='181,140 189,140 185,149' fill='#f59e0b'/><line x1='230' y1='52' x2='230' y2='148' stroke='#f59e0b' stroke-width='1.5'/><polygon points='226,140 234,140 230,149' fill='#f59e0b'/><line x1='275' y1='52' x2='275' y2='148' stroke='#f59e0b' stroke-width='1.5'/><polygon points='271,140 279,140 275,149' fill='#f59e0b'/><line x1='320' y1='52' x2='320' y2='148' stroke='#f59e0b' stroke-width='1.5'/><polygon points='316,140 324,140 320,149' fill='#f59e0b'/><line x1='365' y1='52' x2='365' y2='148' stroke='#f59e0b' stroke-width='1.5'/><polygon points='361,140 369,140 365,149' fill='#f59e0b'/><line x1='410' y1='52' x2='410' y2='148' stroke='#f59e0b' stroke-width='1.5'/><polygon points='406,140 414,140 410,149' fill='#f59e0b'/><line x1='455' y1='52' x2='455' y2='148' stroke='#f59e0b' stroke-width='1.5'/><polygon points='451,140 459,140 455,149' fill='#f59e0b'/><line x1='500' y1='52' x2='500' y2='148' stroke='#f59e0b' stroke-width='1.5'/><polygon points='496,140 504,140 500,149' fill='#f59e0b'/><line x1='545' y1='52' x2='545' y2='148' stroke='#f59e0b' stroke-width='1.5'/><polygon points='541,140 549,140 545,149' fill='#f59e0b'/><rect x='95' y='150' width='450' height='15' rx='2' fill='#1e293b' stroke='#e2e8f0' stroke-width='2'/><polygon points='95,165 82,192 108,192' fill='none' stroke='#38bdf8' stroke-width='2'/><line x1='82' y1='192' x2='74' y2='202' stroke='#94a3b8' stroke-width='1.4'/><line x1='91' y1='192' x2='83' y2='202' stroke='#94a3b8' stroke-width='1.4'/><line x1='99' y1='192' x2='91' y2='202' stroke='#94a3b8' stroke-width='1.4'/><line x1='108' y1='192' x2='100' y2='202' stroke='#94a3b8' stroke-width='1.4'/><text x='95' y='144' fill='#7dd3fc' font-size='15' font-weight='700' text-anchor='middle'>A</text><polygon points='545,165 532,188 558,188' fill='none' stroke='#38bdf8' stroke-width='2'/><circle cx='538' cy='194' r='5' fill='none' stroke='#38bdf8' stroke-width='1.8'/><circle cx='552' cy='194' r='5' fill='none' stroke='#38bdf8' stroke-width='1.8'/><line x1='530' y1='200' x2='560' y2='200' stroke='#94a3b8' stroke-width='1.6'/><text x='545' y='144' fill='#7dd3fc' font-size='15' font-weight='700' text-anchor='middle'>B</text><line x1='95' y1='228' x2='545' y2='228' stroke='#94a3b8' stroke-width='1.4'/><polygon points='95,228 106,223 106,233' fill='#94a3b8'/><polygon points='545,228 534,223 534,233' fill='#94a3b8'/><text x='320' y='219' fill='#cbd5e1' font-size='14' text-anchor='middle'>8 m</text></svg><figcaption>Viga biapoyada de 8 m con carga uniforme de 200 N/m en toda su longitud.</figcaption></figure>",
     "aplica_html": "<p>Por simetría \\(R_A=R_B=\\frac{qL}{2}\\). El cortante \\(V(x)=R_A-qx\\) varía linealmente y el momento \\(M(x)=R_Ax-\\frac{qx^2}{2}\\) es parabólico, máximo en el centro donde el cortante se anula.</p>",
     "solucion_html": "<p>Datos: \\(q=200\\,\\mathrm{N/m}\\), \\(L=8\\,\\mathrm{m}\\).</p><h5>Reacciones</h5><div class='formula'>$$R_A=R_B=\\frac{qL}{2}=\\frac{200\\cdot 8}{2}=800\\,\\mathrm{N}$$</div><h5>a) Ecuaciones (origen en A)</h5><div class='formula'>$$V(x)=800-200\\,x\\quad(\\mathrm{N})\\qquad M(x)=800\\,x-100\\,x^2\\quad(\\mathrm{N\\cdot m})$$</div><h5>Valores máximos</h5><p>El cortante se anula en \\(x=4\\,\\mathrm{m}\\):</p><div class='formula'>$$V_{max}=800\\,\\mathrm{N}\\;(\\text{en apoyos})\\qquad M_{max}=800\\cdot 4-100\\cdot 4^2=1600\\,\\mathrm{N\\cdot m}$$</div><div class='res'><b>V<sub>máx</sub> = 800 N &nbsp;·&nbsp; M<sub>máx</sub> = 1600 N&middot;m (centro)</b></div><h5>b) Diagramas</h5><figure class='fig'><svg viewBox='0 0 560 300' width='100%' style='max-width:520px;height:auto' fill='none' font-family='Inter,system-ui,sans-serif'><line x1='65' y1='70' x2='530' y2='70' stroke='#94a3b8' stroke-width='1.4'/><text x='65' y='28' fill='#e2e8f0' font-size='13'>V (N)</text><polygon points='70,70 70,34 520,106 520,70' fill='rgba(56,189,248,.16)' stroke='none'/><line x1='70' y1='34' x2='520' y2='106' stroke='#38bdf8' stroke-width='2.4'/><line x1='70' y1='70' x2='70' y2='34' stroke='#38bdf8' stroke-width='2.4'/><line x1='520' y1='106' x2='520' y2='70' stroke='#38bdf8' stroke-width='2.4'/><text x='78' y='40' fill='#7dd3fc' font-size='12'>+800</text><text x='512' y='118' fill='#7dd3fc' font-size='12' text-anchor='end'>-800</text><text x='295' y='84' fill='#94a3b8' font-size='11' text-anchor='middle'>x=4 m</text><line x1='65' y1='240' x2='530' y2='240' stroke='#94a3b8' stroke-width='1.4'/><text x='65' y='148' fill='#e2e8f0' font-size='13'>M (N·m)</text><polygon points='70,240 70.0,240.0 75.6,236.1 81.2,232.2 86.9,228.4 92.5,224.8 98.1,221.2 103.8,217.8 109.4,214.4 115.0,211.2 120.6,208.1 126.2,205.0 131.9,202.1 137.5,199.2 143.1,196.4 148.8,193.8 154.4,191.2 160.0,188.8 165.6,186.4 171.2,184.2 176.9,182.1 182.5,180.0 188.1,178.1 193.8,176.2 199.4,174.4 205.0,172.8 210.6,171.2 216.2,169.8 221.9,168.4 227.5,167.2 233.1,166.1 238.8,165.0 244.4,164.1 250.0,163.2 255.6,162.4 261.2,161.8 266.9,161.2 272.5,160.8 278.1,160.4 283.8,160.2 289.4,160.1 295.0,160.0 300.6,160.1 306.2,160.2 311.9,160.4 317.5,160.8 323.1,161.2 328.8,161.8 334.4,162.4 340.0,163.2 345.6,164.1 351.2,165.0 356.9,166.1 362.5,167.2 368.1,168.4 373.8,169.8 379.4,171.2 385.0,172.8 390.6,174.4 396.2,176.2 401.9,178.1 407.5,180.0 413.1,182.1 418.8,184.2 424.4,186.4 430.0,188.8 435.6,191.2 441.2,193.8 446.9,196.4 452.5,199.2 458.1,202.1 463.8,205.0 469.4,208.1 475.0,211.2 480.6,214.4 486.2,217.8 491.9,221.2 497.5,224.8 503.1,228.4 508.8,232.2 514.4,236.1 520.0,240.0 520,240' fill='rgba(74,222,128,.18)' stroke='none'/><polyline points='70.0,240.0 75.6,236.1 81.2,232.2 86.9,228.4 92.5,224.8 98.1,221.2 103.8,217.8 109.4,214.4 115.0,211.2 120.6,208.1 126.2,205.0 131.9,202.1 137.5,199.2 143.1,196.4 148.8,193.8 154.4,191.2 160.0,188.8 165.6,186.4 171.2,184.2 176.9,182.1 182.5,180.0 188.1,178.1 193.8,176.2 199.4,174.4 205.0,172.8 210.6,171.2 216.2,169.8 221.9,168.4 227.5,167.2 233.1,166.1 238.8,165.0 244.4,164.1 250.0,163.2 255.6,162.4 261.2,161.8 266.9,161.2 272.5,160.8 278.1,160.4 283.8,160.2 289.4,160.1 295.0,160.0 300.6,160.1 306.2,160.2 311.9,160.4 317.5,160.8 323.1,161.2 328.8,161.8 334.4,162.4 340.0,163.2 345.6,164.1 351.2,165.0 356.9,166.1 362.5,167.2 368.1,168.4 373.8,169.8 379.4,171.2 385.0,172.8 390.6,174.4 396.2,176.2 401.9,178.1 407.5,180.0 413.1,182.1 418.8,184.2 424.4,186.4 430.0,188.8 435.6,191.2 441.2,193.8 446.9,196.4 452.5,199.2 458.1,202.1 463.8,205.0 469.4,208.1 475.0,211.2 480.6,214.4 486.2,217.8 491.9,221.2 497.5,224.8 503.1,228.4 508.8,232.2 514.4,236.1 520.0,240.0' fill='none' stroke='#4ade80' stroke-width='2.4'/><line x1='295' y1='240' x2='295' y2='160' stroke='#4ade80' stroke-width='1' stroke-dasharray='4 3'/><text x='295' y='154' fill='#86efac' font-size='12' text-anchor='middle'>1600</text><text x='70' y='258' fill='#94a3b8' font-size='12' text-anchor='middle'>A</text><text x='520' y='258' fill='#94a3b8' font-size='12' text-anchor='middle'>B</text></svg><figcaption>Cortante lineal (de +800 a &minus;800 N) y momento flector parabólico (máx. 1600 N&middot;m).</figcaption></figure>"
