     "enunciado_html": "<p>Simplifica el siguiente sistema de control hasta conseguir la función de transferencia. <span class='pts'>(2,5 puntos)</span></p>",
     "figura_enunciado_svg": "<figure class='fig'><svg viewBox='0 0 900 360' width='100%' style='max-width:820px;height:auto' fill='none' stroke='#cbd5e1' stroke-width='2' font-family='Inter,system-ui,sans-serif' font-size='14'><defs><marker id='ar' markerWidth='9' markerHeight='8' refX='7' refY='3' orient='auto'><path d='M0,0 L7,3 L0,6 Z' fill='#cbd5e1'/></marker></defs><line x1='70' y1='185' x2='94' y2='185' stroke='#cbd5e1' marker-end='url(#ar)'/><circle cx='110' cy='185' r='15' stroke='#e2e8f0'/><line x1='100' y1='174' x2='120' y2='196' stroke='#94a3b8'/><line x1='120' y1='174' x2='100' y2='196' stroke='#94a3b8'/><line x1='126' y1='185' x2='170' y2='185' stroke='#cbd5e1' marker-end='url(#ar)'/><rect x='170' y='163' width='80' height='44' rx='5' stroke='#22d3ee'/><text x='210.0' y='190.0' fill='#e2e8f0' font-size='15' text-anchor='middle'>G1</text><line x1='250' y1='185' x2='292' y2='185' stroke='#cbd5e1' marker-end='url(#ar)'/><rect x='292' y='163' width='80' height='44' rx='5' stroke='#22d3ee'/><text x='332.0' y='190.0' fill='#e2e8f0' font-size='15' text-anchor='middle'>G2</text><line x1='372' y1='185' x2='470' y2='185' stroke='#cbd5e1' marker-end='url(#ar)'/><circle cx='412' cy='185' r='3.2' fill='#cbd5e1' stroke='none'/><rect x='470' y='163' width='80' height='44' rx='5' stroke='#22d3ee'/><text x='510.0' y='190.0' fill='#e2e8f0' font-size='15' text-anchor='middle'>G3</text><line x1='550' y1='185' x2='632' y2='185' stroke='#cbd5e1' marker-end='url(#ar)'/><rect x='470' y='78' width='80' height='44' rx='5' stroke='#22d3ee'/><text x='510.0' y='105.0' fill='#e2e8f0' font-size='15' text-anchor='middle'>G4</text><line x1='412' y1='185' x2='412' y2='100' stroke='#cbd5e1'/><line x1='412' y1='100' x2='470' y2='100' stroke='#cbd5e1' marker-end='url(#ar)'/><line x1='550' y1='100' x2='632' y2='100' stroke='#cbd5e1'/><line x1='632' y1='100' x2='648' y2='167' stroke='#cbd5e1' marker-end='url(#ar)'/><circle cx='650' cy='185' r='15' stroke='#e2e8f0'/><line x1='640' y1='174' x2='660' y2='196' stroke='#94a3b8'/><line x1='660' y1='174' x2='640' y2='196' stroke='#94a3b8'/><line x1='666' y1='185' x2='760' y2='185' stroke='#cbd5e1' marker-end='url(#ar)'/><text x='40' y='190' fill='#e2e8f0' font-size='16' text-anchor='start'>U</text><text x='772' y='190' fill='#e2e8f0' font-size='16' text-anchor='start'>V</text><text x='92' y='171' fill='#4ade80' font-size='14' text-anchor='start'>+</text><text x='96' y='211' fill='#4ade80' font-size='14' text-anchor='start'>+</text><text x='632' y='171' fill='#4ade80' font-size='14' text-anchor='start'>+</text><text x='636' y='211' fill='#4ade80' font-size='14' text-anchor='start'>+</text><rect x='250' y='272' width='82' height='40' rx='5' stroke='#a78bfa'/><text x='291.0' y='297.0' fill='#e2e8f0' font-size='15' text-anchor='middle'>H1</text><line x1='412' y1='185' x2='412' y2='292' stroke='#cbd5e1'/><line x1='412' y1='292' x2='332' y2='292' stroke='#cbd5e1'/><line x1='250' y1='292' x2='110' y2='292' stroke='#cbd5e1'/><line x1='110' y1='292' x2='110' y2='203' stroke='#cbd5e1' marker-end='url(#ar)'/></svg><figcaption>Cadena G<sub>1</sub>G<sub>2</sub> con H<sub>1</sub> en realimentación positiva y dos ramas de salida en paralelo (G<sub>3</sub> y G<sub>4</sub>).</figcaption></figure>",
     "aplica_html": "<p>Los bloques \\(G_3\\) y \\(G_4\\) están en <b>paralelo</b> (mismo origen, se suman): equivalen a \\(G_3+G_4\\). El lazo positivo de \\(G_1G_2\\) con \\(H_1\\) da \\(\\frac{G_1G_2}{1-G_1G_2H_1}\\).</p>",
     "solucion_html": "<h5>Lazo interno (H<sub>1</sub>, positivo)</h5><p>Sea \\(N\\) la señal tras \\(G_2\\): \\(N=G_1G_2(U+H_1N)\\Rightarrow N=\\dfrac{G_1G_2}{1-G_1G_2H_1}\\,U\\).</p><h5>Ramas en paralelo</h5><p>La salida es \\(V=(G_3+G_4)\\,N\\):</p><div class='formula'>$$\\boxed{\\dfrac{V}{U}=\\dfrac{G_1G_2\\,(G_3+G_4)}{1-G_1G_2H_1}}$$</div><div class='res'><b>V/U = G<sub>1</sub>G<sub>2</sub>(G<sub>3</sub> + G<sub>4</sub>) / (1 − G<sub>1</sub>G<sub>2</sub>H<sub>1</sub>)</b></div>"
    }
   ]
